{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "famnotify-full-api-collection",
    "name": "FamNotify Full API",
    "description": "Comprehensive API collection for FamNotify.\n\n### Folders\n- **Auth**: User authentication.\n- **User**: Profile management.\n- **Admin**: Group-level administration (Announcements, Events, Members).\n- **Super Admin**: System-wide statistics (Restricted to super-admin email).\n- **Cron**: Background job triggers.\n\n### Authentication\n1. Run **Auth > Login**.\n2. The `access_token` is saved automatically.\n3. Ensure `familyGroupId`, `eventId`, and `base_url` variables are set.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.session) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.session.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refresh_token\", jsonData.session.refresh_token);",
                  "    console.log(\"Access Token saved!\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"your-password\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign Up (Create User)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"securepassword\",\n    \"name\": \"משתמש חדש\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/create-user",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "create-user"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
